是一個致力於在全球範圍促進民主自由發展的非盈利無黨派組織。國際共和學會在去年12月被北京宣佈為制裁對象。今年8月10日，該學會會長特維寧（Daniel Twining）等5人被中共定為製裁對象。蓬佩奧稱&ldquo;這些制裁是榮譽的徽章。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"539fd39d15caae2c7581e9851d27fb80f8333568","tid":2243544,"uid":310700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a988843d56236299ce8251f234a736fe12a9a8a","tid":2243544,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T01:52:50.000Z","msg":"再見啦 蓬佩奧<br />\n唉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T08:53:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}